    "text": "Guaranteeing Retention and Aid During Shutdowns Act or the GRAD Act\n\nThis bill prohibits institutions of higher education\u00a0that participate in federal student aid programs from terminating or otherwise altering the enrollment status of a student due to a disruption of the student\u00e2\u20ac\u2122s federal student financial aid caused by a lapse in appropriations (i.e., government shutdown)."
